title: Hour 2: The Hurts Locker
description:
Stephen A., Jeremy Fowler, Marcus Spears, and Bart Scott question the Dolphins leadership in regards to Tua's head injury, look at Jalen Hurts' opportunity in Philly and if the Nets are positioned to win the East in the NBA.
